text: Kenichi Kumagai (born 17 March 1927) is a Japanese former sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Japanese male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Japan Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Aichi Prefecture
